From fed868cf11c37c0796742dcbf3dbd3a5c0f87146 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: VLM Build Fix <vlm-bot@build.fix>
Date: Sun, 14 Jun 2026 07:42:35 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] fix: resolve all build-blocking bugs for APK compilation
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

CRITICAL FIXES:
- BugLogger: rename public fun logFile() → getLogFile() to resolve Kotlin name
  clash with private var logFile (JVM platform declaration clash = compile error)
- VideoSearchScreen: fix bad import 'androidx.compose.foundation.Image' (wrong pkg),
  rewrite with clean non-conflicting import block
- VideoSearchScreen: remove invalid initialValue param on StateFlow.collectAsStateWithLifecycle()
- VideoDatabase MIGRATION_2_3: remove manual FTS table creation; Room @Fts4 generates
  the virtual table and sync triggers automatically after migration (manual SQL caused
  identity hash mismatch and potential duplicate table errors)
- themes.xml: change parent from android:Theme.Material.Light.NoActionBar (legacy)
  to Theme.MaterialComponents.DayNight.NoActionBar (correct AppCompat/M3 bridge)
- app/build.gradle.kts: add com.google.android.material:material:1.12.0 dependency
  required by new themes.xml parent; bump coil3 rc01 → 3.0.4 stable

OTHER FIXES:
- VideoPlayerScreen: update LocalLifecycleOwner import from deprecated
  androidx.compose.ui.platform → androidx.lifecycle.compose (lifecycle 2.8.x)
- MainNavigationShell: fix bottom bar visibility — was comparing currentRoute against
  route template 'player/{encodedPath}' which never matches; changed to startsWith()
- SettingsScreen: remove unused AnimatedVisibility/expandVertically/shrinkVertically imports
- LogViewerScreen: update BugLogger.logFile() call → BugLogger.getLogFile()
- Schema: add missing 2.json (Room requires all intermediate version schemas present)
